<h2 class="option option--mix">Mix your options</h2>

<h3>Key facts</h3>

<ol class="ordered-list">
  <li>You can mix your options, eg use some of your pot to get an adjustable income and some to buy an annuity.</li>
  <li>Not all providers offer all the options.</li>
  <li>If you have multiple pots, you can use different options for each pot, eg leave one pot untouched and take cash in chunks from another.</li>
</ol>

